page.title: 19FLORA/FAUNA of Blindcrake
page.content: The following have been recorded: Agrimony, Birds foot trefoil, Bluebell Butter cup, Campion Red, Celendin Chickweed,Clover,Coltsfoot, Columbine, Cowslip, Cuckoo Pint, Convolvulus, Daisy,Deadly Night shade,Early Purple Orchid, Field Poppy, Forget-me-not, Gorse, Groundsel, Honey suckle, Ivy, Ivyleaved Toad Flax Jack by the hedge, Ladys' Smock, Lung wort, Mallow, Meadowcranes bill,Nettle,Ox Eye Daisy, Primrose, Pyramidal Orchis, Ribwort Plantain,Rosebay Willowherb, Scabious, Self-heal, Shepherds Purse, Snowdrop, Spotted Orchis, Twayblade, Vetch, Violet, Water Avens, Welsh Poppy, Wild Rose, Wild Strawberry, Wood Avens,Wood Anenome, Yellow Iris. Ash,Beech,Blackthorn,Bird Cherry, Crab Apple,Elder,Hawthorn,Hazel,Horse Chestnut,Larch,Oak,Sloe,Wild Cherry, Willow
